  <brief_title>Hydroxycobalamin and Rural Emergency Medical Services Cyanide Exposure Patients: A Cost Analysis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Hydroxycobalamin and Rural Emergency Medical Services Cyanide Exposure Patients: A Cost Analysis</official_title>
